                        <interp inst="t18370612-name-426" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM DICKINSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I found three marked shillings on the prisoner.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
